To execute griffin follow the steps below

Linux:

1. Grant the griffin script execution permission:

  chmod +x griffin

2. Run the script with -h option for help

  ./griffin -h

3. Examples can be found in examples/queries folder, to query Griffin with akutsu.grf type the following
  
  griffin -f akutsu.grf -o akutsu.out



